I said let him go!

131
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,880
Drag him out!

132
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:39,640
Your Majesty!

133
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:40,480
Your Majesty, spare me!

134
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:42,000
Your Majesty, spare me!

135
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,880
Crown Prince Li Chi.

136
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,960
I'm old now

137
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,920
