138
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:53,160
In consideration
of our father-son relationship...

139
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,000
Father,

140
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,520
at a time like this,

141
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,520
