142
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,440
How ridiculous!

143
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:11,040
You don't actually think
I've lost, do you?

144
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:11,960
You...

145
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,840
Na Jinci, kill him!

146
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,040
Don't forget,

147
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:30,440
