148
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,560
Do you still need to hesitate
about who to choose?

149
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:35,160
You want me to kill the Emperor?

150
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,080
All the courtiers

151
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:38,960
