156
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,160
Na Jinci,

157
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,280
I know you too well.

158
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,920
Someone like you

159
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:01,760
