than survive in disgrace.

163
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,120
You're crazy!

164
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,360
I'd rather die

165
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:40,280
than betray my heart's desire.

166
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,240
