169
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,320
If everything

170
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,760
was already destined,

171
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,360
I'd rather die by your hand.

172
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:09,040
You don't deserve a peaceful death.

173
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:12,080
I'll send you to hell

174
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,640
