186
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:10,200
Xie Wanyin,

187
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,240
I want you to never forget me

188
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:16,240
for all your lifetimes.

189
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,840
Na Jinci,

190
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,280
I'll be waiting for you

191
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:42,760
