207
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:09,720
What if we grind the bracelet
into powder

208
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,000
and use it as the catalyst?

209
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:12,760
Or maybe...

210
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:13,440
maybe

211
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:14,840
