214
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:22,080
I was too careless.

215
00:15:22,400 --> 00:15:23,520
It's all my fault.

216
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:26,600
How could Li Chi not have a backup plan?

217
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,800
